TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Bias and Moment Matrix of the General k-Class Estimators of the Parameters in Simultaneous Equations
AU  - Nagar, A. L.
AB  - [In this article we study the small sample properties of the so called general k-class estimators of simultaneous equations. Two members of the family of k-class estimators are found, one of which is unbiased to the degree of our approximation and the other possesses a minimum second moment around the true parameter value, again to the order of our approximation.]
C1  - Full publication date: Oct., 1959
