TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Dynamic Properties of the Klein-Goldberger Model
AU  - Adelman, Irma
AU  - Adelman, Frank L.
AB  - [The authors examine the dynamic properties of the Klein-Goldberger model of the United States economy by extrapolating the exogenous variables and solving the equations on the IBM 650 for one hundred years. In this process no indication was found of oscillatory behavior. The introduction of random impulses of a reasonable order of magnitude, however, generates cycles which are comparable in their properties to those of the United States economy.]
C1  - Full publication date: Oct., 1959
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1909353
